{"data":[{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037601787285549441"],"id":"2037601787285549441","text":"Claude Codeあるあるですが、複数セッション起動してると通知音が鳴るたびにモグラ叩きみたいに確認・修正・指示を繰り返して時間が溶けてしまう。\n\nお風呂入ろう、ご飯食べよう、寝ようと思いつつ、あと1ラリーだけ...と思いながら3時間くらい経過してることはザラにあります。 https://t.co/XBaAYZ494T","author_id":"3120155797","created_at":"2026-03-27T18:44:57.000Z","entities":{"urls":[{"start":139,"end":162,"url":"https://t.co/XBaAYZ494T","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/masahirochaen/status/2034282341745807765","display_url":"x.com/masahirochaen/…"}]},"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":3,"like_count":18,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":6,"impression_count":5271}},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037560786378530929"],"id":"2037560786378530929","text":"私が使っている「Claude Code × MCP」の連携設定。\nよければ参考にしてください！！\n\nMCP連携を6カテゴリーに整理しました\uD83D\uDC47\n\n\uD83D\uDEE0 開発支援\n・GitHub, Figma, Playwright\n・コード生成〜デバッグまで全部AI\n\n\uD83C\uDFA8 デザイン\n・Canva, Excalidraw, Mermaid\n・構成図もUIもClaude Codeから直接生成\n\n\uD83D\uDCC4 https://t.co/iyKdyWBPTL","author_id":"3120155797","created_at":"2026-03-27T16:02:02.000Z","entities":{"urls":[{"start":189,"end":212,"url":"https://t.co/iyKdyWBPTL","expanded_url":"https://x.com/masahirochaen/status/2037560786378530929/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/iyKdyWBPTL","media_key":"3_2037546621341483008"}]},"public_metrics":{"retweet_count":21,"reply_count":4,"like_count":276,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":359,"impression_count":13211}},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037524795936662007"],"id":"2037524795936662007","text":"【\uD83D\uDD25朗報】 Googleのリアルタイム音声AIがアップデート\n\n・Gemini 3.1 Flash Liveが最新モデルに\n・会話の記憶が従来比2倍、長い議論でも文脈を維持\n・レイテンシ改善＋背景ノイズ除去も強化\n・90言語以上対応、Search Liveが200カ国以上に展開\n\n日本語性能＋検索も良い感じ\nhttps://t.co/GP3hfsgEGu","author_id":"3120155797","created_at":"2026-03-27T13:39:01.000Z","entities":{"urls":[{"start":155,"end":178,"url":"https://t.co/GP3hfsgEGu","expanded_url":"https://x.com/GeminiApp/status/2037190629999206673/video/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/GP3hfsgEGu","media_key":"13_2037185605835